Meeting 1.2 – Requirements Gathering
Date: 03 March 2026
Time: 11:00 – 11:30
Attendees: All Members
Agenda:
Identify system requirements
Define user roles and permissions
Discussion:
The functional requirements of the system were discussed in detail. Three main user roles were identified: Admin, Staff, and Customer. Each role was assigned specific responsibilities. Admin would manage car records, Staff would handle hiring and returning of cars, and Customers would search and view available cars. Additional system features such as searching by price and viewing available cars were also confirmed.
Outcome:
Functional requirements finalised
User roles and responsibilities clearly defined
